  "short_description": "Weatherproof junction box for UniFi Bullet, Dome, and Turret cameras. Tamper-resistant design. Supports side and rear 3/4\" conduit entrances. Constructed with aluminium and polycarbonate.",
  "description": "The Ubiquiti Camera Junction Box provides a robust and secure mounting solution for your UniFi Bullet, Dome, and Turret cameras. The tamper-resistant design discourages unauthorized access and safeguards your camera and its cabling. The sleek design complements the modern aesthetic of UniFi cameras, creating a professional look for your installation. With its focus on security, aesthetics, and functionality, the Ubiquiti Camera Junction Box empowers you to seamlessly integrate your UniFi cameras into your surveillance system.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Secure Mounting",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Camera Junction Box provides a robust and secure mounting solution for your UniFi Bullet, Dome, and Turret cameras. The tamper-resistant design discourages unauthorized access and safeguards your camera and its cabling. The sleek design complements the modern aesthetic of UniFi cameras, creating a professional look for your installation. With its focus on security, aesthetics, and functionality, the Ubiquiti Camera Junction Box empowers you to seamlessly integrate your UniFi cameras into your surveillance system."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Flexible Mounting Options",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Camera Junction Box offers versatility for various mounting configurations. This junction box provides the flexibility to mount your camera on various surfaces, including flat walls, poles, or using a pendant mount (sold separately). Conveniently route your cables through the side and rear 3/4\" conduit entrances for a clean and organized installation. You can easily access wiring connections whenever necessary, ensuring your security system remains functional."
    }
  ],
